NordLocker is the world’s leading end-to-end encrypted cloud for business and personal use. It was created by the cybersecurity experts behind NordVPN – one of the world’s most advanced VPN service providers. NordLocker is available on Windows, macOS, Android, iOS, and web browsers.
The platform supports all file types and guarantees secure sync between devices. With NordLocker, your files are encrypted with a unique key that gives you complete access control. Allowing you to share the encrypted files, the platform ensures secure data management.